    "raw_ingredients": "DIMETHYL ETHER • ALCOHOL DENAT. • VA/CROTONATES/VINYL NEODECANOATE COPOLYMER • OCTYLACRYLAMIDE/ACRYLATES/BUTYLAMINOETHYL METHACRYLATE COPOLYMER • AQUA / WATER • ASCORBYL GLUCOSIDE • ACETYL CEDRENE • POGOSTEMON CABLIN OIL • AMINOMETHYL PROPANOL • TRIMETHYLBENZENEPROPANOL • LIMONENE • LINALYL ACETATE • BENZYL ALCOHOL • LINALOOL • PINENE • CARVONE • TERPINEOL • CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL • TETRAMETHYL ACETYLOCTAHYDRONAPHTHALENES • CITRONELLOL • CITRAL • HEXYL CINNAMAL • PARFUM / FRAGRANCE (F.I.L. Z70077626/2).",
